ticker	holdings_when	prices_when	shares	price
APPL	2001-01-01 00:00:30	2001-01-01 00:00:00	2.94	1
APPL	2001-01-01 00:01:30	2001-01-01 00:01:00	24.13	2
GOOG	2001-01-01 00:00:30	2001-01-01 00:00:00	23.45	1
